00:35:21,585 --> 00:35:26,670
because he was that fundamental to our understanding of how the mind works,

531
00:35:26,930 --> 00:35:29,473
the neuroscience behind it, the experiences behind it,

532
00:35:30,113 --> 00:35:34,117
and he helped shape the development of the project in a deep and fundamental way.

533
00:35:37,364 --> 00:35:39,486
So to break it down, visual perception.

