00:38:20,556 --> 00:38:23,338
To her, she would see the flashback appear around her forming.

576
00:38:25,416 --> 00:38:27,397
from something that might start off unclear,

577
00:38:27,837 --> 00:38:29,218
and then she would get drawn in

578
00:38:29,278 --> 00:38:31,159
and start to relive that experience.

579
00:38:31,179 --> 00:38:33,161
So it's not like films where you get lots of fast cuts.

580
00:38:33,801 --> 00:38:37,163
It was more like you're just sucked into a new reality.

581
00:38:37,243 --> 00:38:38,824
And I could relate to that somewhat.

582
00:38:38,864 --> 00:38:41,586
So if you think of times where you're dreaming

583
00:38:42,006 --> 00:38:43,787
and then your dream just transitions

584
00:38:43,827 --> 00:38:45,728
from one moment to another seamlessly,

585
00:38:45,748 --> 00:38:46,469
and you're just drawn in,

