00:39:08,996 --> 00:39:11,218
was that this would be terribly confusing.

592
00:39:11,959 --> 00:39:16,303
But when you think about memories, you don't think about memories in a linear chronological

593
00:39:16,383 --> 00:39:18,585
order, you think about the moments that define your life.

594
00:39:19,430 --> 00:39:24,434
that's what matters, the impact those moments, those scenes in your life experience have on you.

