00:40:52,530 --> 00:41:02,520
when talking to them. It clearly did not apply to them. And I really felt

616
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:06,043
their frustration because they don't consider themselves mentally ill.

617
00:41:06,123 --> 00:41:06,884
They hear voices.

